    "title": "Agentic SEO in 2026: How OpenAI Operator, Claude Computer Use, and Cursor Agents Are Replacing Manual Ecommerce SEO Work",
    "description": "Explore how agentic AI tools like OpenAI Operator, Claude Computer Use, and Cursor agents are automating ecommerce SEO workflows in 2026.",
    "published": "2026-01-02T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Industry Insights",
