    "title": "AHPRA-Safe Content That Ranks: AI SEO for Australian Health and Supplement Shopify Stores",
    "description": "Learn how to create AHPRA-compliant AI SEO content for Australian health and supplement Shopify stores that ranks in Google without risking regulatory penalties.",
    "published": "2025-11-03T12:00:00.000Z",
