    "title": "AI Agent Skills for Ecommerce Marketing: What They Are and Why They Matter for Shopify in 2026",
    "description": "Learn what AI agent skills are, how they work, and why they're transforming ecommerce marketing for Shopify stores with autonomous, reusable AI capabilities.",
    "published": "2026-02-08T14:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Growth Marketing",
