    "title": "Building AI Agent Skills for Shopify SEO: A Practical Guide for Non-Technical Marketers",
    "description": "A step-by-step guide for non-technical marketers to build AI agent skills that automate Shopify SEO tasks like content creation, schema markup, and reporting.",
    "published": "2026-02-07T14:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "SEO Strategy",
