    "title": "ChatGPT Search Is the New Google: How to Optimize Your Ecommerce Store for OpenAI's Search Engine in 2026",
    "description": "Learn how to optimize your ecommerce store for ChatGPT Search, OpenAI's AI-powered search engine that's reshaping how consumers discover and buy products.",
    "published": "2026-01-20T12:00:00.000Z",
