    "title": "Claude 4.6 Opus for Shopify Collection Pages: Long-Form Category Content That Wins AI Overviews and Converts",
    "description": "Use Anthropic's Claude 4.6 Opus to generate long-form Shopify collection page content that ranks in Google AI Overviews and drives conversions.",
    "published": "2026-02-08T10:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "E-commerce",
