    "title": "Cursor Agents for Shopify Migrations: Auto-Generate Redirect Maps, QA Broken Links, and Validate Schema Post-Launch",
    "description": "Use Cursor AI agents to automate Shopify migration tasks including redirect mapping, broken link detection, and schema validation for zero-traffic-loss migrations.",
