    "title": "Cyber Monday SEO for Shopify: Last-Minute AI Tactics That Drive Organic Sales",
    "description": "Last-minute Cyber Monday SEO tactics for Shopify stores. Use AI to optimize deal pages, meta tags, and schema markup for maximum organic visibility.",
    "published": "2025-11-15T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "E-commerce",
