    "title": "Enterprise Shopify SEO: AI Workflows for Brands with 10,000+ SKUs Across Regions",
    "description": "Enterprise-scale Shopify SEO strategies using AI workflows. Manage 10,000+ SKUs across multiple regions with automated content, schema, and monitoring.",
