    "title": "Grow Your Email List with Shopify SEO: AI Content Funnels That Convert Readers to Subscribers",
    "description": "Use AI-powered SEO content funnels on Shopify to grow your email list organically. Convert blog readers and product browsers into email subscribers.",
    "published": "2025-12-05T12:00:00.000Z",
