    "title": "How to Reduce Customer Acquisition Cost with AI SEO: Organic vs Paid for Shopify",
    "description": "Learn how AI-powered SEO reduces customer acquisition costs on Shopify by building organic traffic that compounds, replacing expensive paid ad dependency.",
    "published": "2025-10-28T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Growth Marketing",
