    "title": "Ingredient Search to Add-to-Cart: AI-Powered SEO for Skincare and Beauty Brands on Shopify",
    "description": "Learn how AI SEO helps Shopify skincare and beauty brands rank for ingredient-driven queries and convert ingredient-savvy shoppers into customers.",
