    "title": "New Year, New Rankings: AI SEO Resolutions That Drive Shopify Revenue in Q1",
    "description": "Start the new year with AI SEO resolutions for your Shopify store. Practical Q1 strategies that build organic traffic and revenue from January onwards.",
