    "title": "OpenAI Deep Research for Competitive SEO Analysis: Let AI Spend 30 Minutes So You Don't Spend 30 Hours",
    "description": "Use OpenAI Deep Research to automate competitive SEO analysis, uncovering competitor strategies, content gaps, and ranking opportunities in minutes.",
    "published": "2026-01-16T12:00:00.000Z",
