    "title": "Recipe Pages, Farm Stories, and FSANZ Compliance: AI SEO for Shopify Food and Beverage Brands",
    "description": "AI SEO strategies for Shopify food and beverage brands. Learn how to rank with recipe content, origin stories, and FSANZ-compliant product descriptions.",
