    "title": "Shopify Black Friday SEO: The 30-Day AI Sprint to Rank Before the Biggest Shopping Day",
    "description": "A 30-day AI-powered SEO sprint for Shopify stores preparing for Black Friday. Rank for deal queries, gift guides, and seasonal keywords before November 29.",
