    "title": "Shopify Plus SEO with Claude 4.6 Opus: Multi-Store, Multi-Locale Content Automation for Enterprise Brands",
    "description": "Scale Shopify Plus SEO across multiple stores and locales with Claude 4.6 Opus for enterprise-grade content automation and consistent brand quality.",
