    "title": "Shopify SEO for Your First Million: AI Strategies from Launch to Product-Market Fit",
    "description": "AI-powered SEO strategies for Shopify stores working toward their first $1M in revenue. From launch to product-market fit, build organic traffic that compounds.",
    "published": "2025-11-27T12:00:00.000Z",
