    "title": "Shopify URL Structure Mistakes That Tank Rankings: /products/ vs /collections/ Explained",
    "description": "Understand Shopify's URL structure issues including /products/ vs /collections/ paths, duplicate URLs, and canonical tag management for SEO.",
    "published": "2025-12-09T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Technical SEO",
