    "title": "Shopify vs BigCommerce SEO: A Head-to-Head Technical and Content Comparison",
    "description": "Compare Shopify and BigCommerce for SEO with a detailed analysis of technical capabilities, content management, speed, and AI readiness for ecommerce.",
