    "title": "Shopify vs Magento SEO: Why Ecommerce Brands Are Migrating for AI-Native Optimization",
    "description": "Compare Shopify and Magento for SEO in 2025. Learn why ecommerce brands are migrating from Magento to Shopify for faster AI-powered SEO results.",
    "published": "2025-12-15T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "SEO Strategy",
