    "title": "The CMO Guide to AI Agent Skills: What Every Marketing Leader Needs to Know in 2026",
    "description": "A strategic guide for CMOs and marketing leaders on AI agent skills — what they are, how they transform marketing teams, and how to adopt them effectively.",
    "published": "2026-02-05T14:00:00.000Z",
