    "title": "The Complete Shopify SEO Audit Checklist for 2025: Every Issue AI Can Find and Fix",
    "description": "The definitive Shopify SEO audit checklist for 2025. Covers technical SEO, content, schema, speed, and mobile — with AI-powered fixes for every issue.",
    "published": "2025-11-07T12:00:00.000Z",
    "category": "Technical SEO",
