    "title": "V0 by Vercel + GPT-5.2 for Shopify Headless Storefronts: Ship Search-Optimized Landing Pages That Pass CWV in Minutes",
    "description": "Use V0 by Vercel and GPT-5.2 to rapidly build SEO-optimized landing pages for Shopify headless storefronts that pass Core Web Vitals.",
