    "title": "Why Neil Patel AI SEO Underperforms on Multimodal Search—and How SearchFit.ai Fixes It",
    "description": "Frustrated with underperforming AI SEO on TikTok, YouTube, and Google Images? See how SearchFit.ai surpasses Neil Patel AI SEO with real multimodal, video, and image optimization.",
    "published": "2025-10-16T20:31:29.000Z",
